      "rotation": 0,
      "content": "春江潮水連海平,海上明月共潮生。This is a mixed CJK/English line that should wrap automatically. 灩灩隨波千萬里,何處春江無月明!編輯器所見與 CLI 產出必須同像素 — pixel-perfect parity is the hardest constraint.",
